des: These are some of the facts or events of IPL so far. IPL or the Indian Premier League is a domestic League that happens in India each year. Players from around the world participate in this event and get a chance to showcase their skills. IPL has proved to be very effective for the emerging domestic players giving them the opportunity to play against some of the biggest stars in Cricket.
